1.1.name: wordpress/udinra-image-sitemap
1.1.description: Adbrite has discontinued Britepic.So please do not use britepic to monetize your images and instead of using this plugin to create image sitemap you can use Udinra All Image Sitemap which is generalized image sitemap generator.
